Induced emf $\quad e_i=\frac{-d \phi}{d t}=-v \frac{d \phi}{d z}$
which gives $\quad e_i=\frac{\mu_0 3 p a^2 v\left(z_0-z\right)}{2\left[a^2+\left(z_0-z\right)^2\right]^{5 / 2}}$

